headline: Fastenal Company Announces Cash Dividend
summary: WINONA, Minn., January 16, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq:FAST) (collectively referred to as 'Fastenal' or by terms such as 'we', 'our', or 'us') reported its board of directors declared a dividend of $0.43 per share to be paid in cash on February 28, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on January 31, 2025. Except for share and per share information, dollar amounts are stated in millions.
